## Go Tools LSP Glob Pattern Matcher

The code in `internal/glob/` is a copy of the LSP-compliant glob pattern matcher used internally by gopls (an `internal/` package, so it cannot be imported as a dependency and is vendored here instead).

- **Source**: https://cs.opensource.google/go/x/tools/+/gopls/v0.14.2:gopls/internal/lsp/glob/glob.go
- **License**: BSD 3-Clause
- **Copyright**: Copyright 2023 The Go Authors
- **Used for**: Matching file watcher registration glob patterns (`**`, `{a,b}`, `[a-z]`, `[!...]`, etc.) per the LSP 3.17 specification
- **Location**: internal/glob/
- **Modifications**: None; copied as-is

